This documentation describes how to install, configure, and use Altoros Cassandra for Pivotal Platform.
Altoros Cassandra for Pivotal Platform registers a service broker on Pivotal Platform and exposes its service plans on the Marketplace.
Developers can provision Cassandra keyspaces by creating instances of service plans using Apps Manager or the cf Command Line Interface (CLI) tool.

## <a id='overview'></a>Overview

Altoros Cassandra for Pivotal Platform includes the following key features:

* Based on [Apache Cassandra](https://cassandra.apache.org/).
* Shared  plan.
* Provisions a Cassandra keyspace for use with one or more Pivotal Platform apps.

